overview:
PropertyXpress.com is a private real estate & investment intelligence agency providing daily market information, insights, as well as company and projects reports. PropertyXpress.com tracks thousands of news, analysis and even rumors from more than 750 sources in 15+ languages, but filters the important information in one place, in English.

Presently, PropertyXpress.com delivers information about investments, developments and construction of industrial, residential, retail, tourism, logistics and office buildings, sports and leisure facilities, as well as infrastructure in the following markets: Russia, Ukraine, Romania, Bulgaria, Serbia, Croatia, Slovenia, Montenegro, Bosnia and Herzegovina, Kosovo, Moldova, Albania and Macedonia.
